finish with a number

00:52:55.580 --> 00:52:59.910 position:56%
of sound recordings showcasing three
different styles of Persian starting

00:52:59.910 --> 00:53:04.260 position:56%
with a few seconds of the Shahnameh,
a few seconds of the lyrical style

00:53:04.260 --> 00:53:08.920
of Rumi, and of course, free verse
poetry of the Persian poetess,

00:53:08.920 --> 00:53:12.690
Fur gh Farrukhz d
in her own voice.

00:53:12.690 --> 00:53:15.220
This recording is from
a collection of stories

00:53:15.220 --> 00:53:17.440
from the Shahnameh by Firdowsi.

00:53:17.440 --> 00:53:19.790
Here is an excerpt from
"The Battle of Kumarth

00:53:19.790 --> 00:53:25.510
with the Demon" narrated
by Parviz Ahur.

